Classification: Reality
Status: Returning Series
Network: MTV ( USA)
Airs: Tuesdays at 10:00 pm
Runtime: 60 Minutes
Premiere: June 21, 2012
Episode Order: 12

"Snooki & JWOWW" follows the two well-known characters of "Jersey Shore" Nicole "Snooki" Polizzi and Jenni "JWOWW" Farley. Each week they travel around Jersey City and move in together. With their romantic relationships on hold, the two "besties" get to have fun and party. However, when Nicole tells Jenni the surpise that she is pregnant, they have to change their plans of drinking and partying to doing things for the soon-to-be birth of Nicole's first born.
